OL,3,CMan accused of killing and
OL,4,Cdismembering friend 'would do it
OL,5,Cagain' court hears
OL,7,FBenjamin Atkins and Debbie Pereira,
OL,8,F29, are both charged with the murder
OL,9,Fof 48-year-old Simon Shotton, whose
OL,10,Fremains were found in packages on the
OL,11,FManor Steps Zig Zag footpath on
OL,12,FBoscombe seafront in Bournemouth,
OL,13,FDorset.
OL,15,FThey are also on trial at Winchester
OL,16,FCrown Court accused of preventing the
OL,17,Fburial of a corpse and perverting the
OL,18,Fcourse of justice.
