OL,3,CMan accused of killing and
OL,4,Cdismembering friend 'would do it
OL,5,Cagain' court hears
OL,7,FPaul Cavin KC, prosecuting, told the
OL,8,Fjury that a member of the public was
OL,9,Ftaking shelter under a tree on the
OL,10,Fcliffside footpath on August 26 when a
OL,11,Fpackage landed with a "thud" beside
OL,12,Fher.
OL,14,FWhen she got closer to the packet
OL,15,Fwhich was wrapped with grey masking
OL,16,Ftape, she "realised that the shape was
OL,17,Fthat of a human foot and some of it
OL,18,Fhad become exposed" and she called
OL,19,Fpolice, the court heard.
