OL,4,Cdismembering friend 'would do it
OL,5,Cagain' court hears
OL,7,FA search by police discovered a second
OL,8,Fpackage ` DNA tests found that body
OL,9,Fparts belonged to Mr Shotton who had
OL,10,Fbeen released from prison in September
OL,11,F2022 having served a sentence for
OL,12,Fsupplying drugs in the Ipswich area.
OL,14,FMr Cavin said the police were informed
OL,15,Fby the probation service that Mr
OL,16,FShotton had moved to Bournemouth after
OL,17,Fhis release and investigations traced
OL,18,Fhis mobile phone to a Cash Creators
OL,19,Fshop in Boscombe and that it had been
OL,20,Fsold to them by Pereira.
