OL,3,CMan accused of killing and
OL,4,Cdismembering friend 'would do it
OL,5,Cagain' court hears
OL,7,FThe prosecutor said that when police
OL,8,Fraided the defendants' home address,
OL,9,FAtkins was found hiding in the garden
OL,10,Fbehind a wheelbarrow.
OL,12,FFurther searches of the garden then
OL,13,Funcovered two black bin bags
OL,14,Fcontaining Mr Shotton's remains.
OL,16,FIn police interview, Pereira told
OL,17,Fdetectives that Mr Shotton was a crack
OL,18,Fand heroin user and had visited their
OL,19,Fflat to take drugs with them.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/9
