OL,5,Cagain' court hears
OL,7,FShe denied knowing Mr Shotton had
OL,8,Fdied, but admitted that he had stayed
OL,9,Fin a tent in their garden and said
OL,10,FAtkins had been cutting wood and
OL,11,Fburning things including his own shoes
OL,12,Fin the fire pit, and that he had also
OL,13,F"bought large black bin liners, bleach
OL,14,Fand silver tape".
OL,16,FMr Cavin said that as the pair were
OL,17,Ftaken in a police van to a
OL,18,Fmagistrates' court hearing, they were
OL,19,Frecorded on a concealed listening
OL,20,Fdevice talking about the dismembered
OL,21,Fbody parts.
