OL,3,CMan accused of killing and
OL,4,Cdismembering friend 'would do it
OL,5,Cagain' court hears
OL,7,FMr Cavin continued: "Ms Pereira asks
OL,8,FMr Atkins 'Do you regret anything?'
OL,10,F"Chillingly, he responds 'I'll look
OL,11,F'em straight in the eye and say, yeah.
OL,12,FI'd do it again and again and again.
OL,13,FIf you let me go today, I'd find
OL,14,Fanother one and do it again.'
OL,16,F"Ms Pereira told Mr Atkins that the
OL,17,Fpolice had taken 'stuff from under my
OL,18,Fnails', and he responded, 'you'd have
OL,19,Fhad nothing, the amount of bleach you
OL,20,Fused'."
