OL,7,FMr Cavin continued: "Ms Pereira also
OL,8,Fsaid in interview that she had asked
OL,9,FMr Atkins 'Did you kill him?' and that
OL,10,Fhe had replied 'Yeah'.
OL,12,F"She also said that he had been
OL,13,Ftelling her that God had told him to
OL,14,Fdo it, which was not what the
OL,15,Frecording had captured."
OL,17,FHe said Pereira went on to say that
OL,18,FAtkins and Mr Shotton had an argument
OL,19,Fabout the deceased not having supplied
OL,20,Fthem with enough drugs for allowing
OL,21,Fhim to stay at their home.
